---

<Layout 
  title="Sobre Nosotros | AstroTickets"
  description="Conoce al equipo detr√°s de la plataforma de eventos m√°s innovadora."
  ogTitle="Sobre Nosotros - AstroTickets"
  ogDescription="Conoce al equipo detr√°s de la plataforma de eventos m√°s innovadora."
  ogImage="/social_preview.jpg"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight text-base-content">
            Revolucionando la forma <br/>
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent">de vivir eventos</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-base-content font-semibold max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 opacity-100">
            En AstroTickets, creemos que la tecnolog√≠a debe ser el puente invisible que te conecta con tus mejores recuerdos.
        </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision Grid -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="card-body p-10">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 text-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="card-title text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-base-content">Nuestra Misi√≥n</h2>
                    <p class="text-base-content text-lg leading-relaxed font-semibold opacity-100">
                        Eliminar las barreras entre los fans y sus artistas favoritos. Creamos una plataforma segura, r√°pida y transparente donde comprar una entrada es tan emocionante como el evento mismo.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="card-body p-10">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/20 text-secondary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                         <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lightbulb"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-1 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"/><path d="M9 18h6"/><path d="M10 22h4"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="card-title text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-base-content">Nuestra Visi√≥n</h2>
                    <p class="text-base-content text-lg leading-relaxed font-semibold opacity-100">
                        Ser el est√°ndar global en ticketing digital, utilizando tecnolog√≠a de punta como Astro y React para garantizar que nunca m√°s te pierdas un "sold out".
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-base-100">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16 text-base-content">Conoce al Equipo</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
              {teamMembers.map((member) => (
                  <div class="group relative cursor-pointer">
                      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[3/4] mb-6 shadow-lg">
                          {/* CORRECCI√ìN: Usamos <Image /> de Astro en lugar de <img> */}
                          <Image 
                            src={member.image} 
                            alt={member.name} 
                            width={400} 
                            height={533}
                            class="object-cover w-full h-full transform transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0"
                          />
                          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end p-6">
                              <p class="text-white text-sm">{member.bio}</p>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-base-content">{member.name}</h3>
                      <p class="text-primary font-medium">{member.role}</p>
                  </div>
              ))}
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech Stack -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 border-t border-base-300">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-base-content">Construido con Tecnolog√≠a del Futuro</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6">
              {techStack.map((tech) => (
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-base-200 transition-colors cursor-default">
                      <span class="text-4xl mb-3">{tech.icon}</span>
                      <span class="font-bold text-sm">{tech.name}</span>
                      <span class="text-xs text-base-content font-medium">{tech.desc}</span>
                  </div>
              ))}
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>
</Layout>